d 'CHORD': Stata module to draw chord diagrams
d Author: Jiajun Zhou (Technical University of Munich) & De Zhou (Nanjing Agricultural University)
d Inspired by R package circlize (Gu et al., 2014, Bioinformatics 30:2811-2812).
